<meta name="assert" content="Test checks that the 'border-right-color' property is animatable."><p><p>Click the square with red border below. Test passes if the color of right border transforms to green gradually not immediately.</p></p><style>
</style>
<p><style>
  #test {
    border: 0px solid red;
    height: 90px;
    transition-duration: 2s;
    transition-property: border-right-color;
    transition-timing-function: linear;
    width: 90px;
  }
</style></p>
